body: "# Semgrep downloaded findings triage batch\n\nSource CSV: Semgrep_Code_Combined_Findings_2026_07_06.csv (local download, not committed)\nDownloaded: 2026-07-06\nFinding count: 40\nRepository: unbraind/pm-cli\n\nThis parent groups the Semgrep Code findings imported from the downloaded CSV so each platform finding has a durable pm issue with source links and triage metadata.\n\nDuplicate check before import: `pm search semgrep --status all --limit 100 --json` returned 0 items, and `rg` found no Semgrep finding IDs or semgrep.dev finding links under `.agents/pm`."
